</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Epistle_to_Philemon" title="Epistle to Philemon">Epistle to Philemon</a>, Pm</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Epistle_to_the_Hebrews" title="Epistle to the Hebrews">Epistle to the Hebrews</a>, He</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="/wiki/General_Epistles" title="General Epistles" class="mw-redirect">General Epistles</a>, also called Jewish Epistles</p>
<ul>
