<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> for example, see<cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLeroy_Zuck.2C_Roy_B._Zuck1991">Leroy Zuck, Roy B. Zuck (1991). <i>Basic Bible Interpretation</i>. Chariot Victor Pub. p.&#160;68. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0896938190" class="internal">ISBN 0-89693-819-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Basic+Bible+Interpretation&amp;rft.aulast=Leroy+Zuck%2C+Roy+B.+Zuck&amp;rft.au=Leroy+Zuck%2C+Roy+B.+Zuck&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B68&amp;rft.pub=Chariot+Victor+Pub&amp;rft.isbn=0-89693-819-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bible"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
