<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFNorman_L._Geisler1979.2C_1980">Norman L. Geisler (1979, 1980). <i>Inerrancy</i>. The Zondervan Corporation. p.&#160;294. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0310392810" class="internal">ISBN 0-310-39281-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Inerrancy&amp;rft.aulast=Norman+L.+Geisler&amp;rft.au=Norman+L.+Geisler&amp;rft.date=1979%2C+1980&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B294&amp;rft.pub=The+Zondervan+Corporation&amp;rft.isbn=0-310-39281-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bible"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFInternational_Council_on_Biblical_Inerrancy1978">International Council on Biblical Inerrancy (1978) (pdf). <i><a href="http://www.churchcouncil.org/ccpdfdocs/01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A&amp;D.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.churchcouncil.org/ccpdfdocs/01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A&amp;D.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Chicago Statement on Biblical Inerrancy</a></i>. International Council on Biblical Inerrancy<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.churchcouncil.org/ccpdfdocs/01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A&amp;D.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.churchcouncil.org/ccpdfdocs/01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A&amp;D.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.churchcouncil.org/ccpdfdocs/01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A&amp;D.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Chicago+Statement+on+Biblical+Inerrancy&amp;rft.aulast=International+Council+on+Biblical+Inerrancy&amp;rft.au=International+Council+on+Biblical+Inerrancy&amp;rft.date=1978&amp;rft.pub=International+Council+on+Biblical+Inerrancy&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchcouncil.org%2Fccpdfdocs%2F01_Biblical_Inerrancy_A%26D.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bible"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Stagg-25">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Stagg_25-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Stagg_25-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Stagg_25-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> Stagg, Frank. <i>New Testament Theology.</i> Nashville: Broadman, 1962. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0805416137" class="internal">ISBN 0805416137</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/03274a.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/03274a.htm" rel="nofollow">Catholic Encyclopedia: Canon of the New Testament</a>: "The idea of a complete and clear-cut canon of the New Testament existing from the beginning, that is from Apostolic times, has no foundation in history. The Canon of the New Testament, like that of the Old, is the result of a development, of a process at once stimulated by disputes with doubters, both within and without the Church, and retarded by certain obscurities and natural hesitations, and which did not reach its final term until the dogmatic definition of the Tridentine Council."</li>
<li id="cite_note-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27" title="">^</a></b> Paula Fredriksen, <i>Augustine and the Jews</i>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780385502702" class="internal">ISBN 9780385502702</a> (<a href="/wiki/2008" title="2008">2008</a>), pages 67-68, 391.</li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFUnited_Bible_Society2008"><a href="/wiki/United_Bible_Society" title="United Bible Society" class="mw-redirect">United Bible Society</a> (2008), <i><a href="http://www.ubs-translations.org/about_us/#c165" class="external text" title="http://www.ubs-translations.org/about_us/#c165" rel="nofollow">Statistical Summary of languages with the Scriptures</a></i><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.ubs-translations.org/about_us/#c165" class="external free" title="http://www.ubs-translations.org/about_us/#c165" rel="nofollow">http://www.ubs-translations.org/about_us/#c165</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved on 2008-03-22</span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Statistical+Summary+of+languages+with+the+Scriptures&amp;rft.aulast=United+Bible+Society&amp;rft.au=United+Bible+Society&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubs-translations.org%2Fabout_us%2F%23c165&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bible"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
